text: ‘We have lost control’? Photo not of Italy’s prime minister during coronavirus crisis, and quote made up
An image shared on Facebook claims Italian Prime Minister Giuseppe Conte said Italy has lost control of the new coronavirus and the country’s only hope remains up in the Sky, God rescue your people.
